---
permalink: /
title: Home
layout: base.njk
description: A living, community-contributed archive of Yoruba proverbs (òwe).
---
<h1>Òwe Yòòbá</h1>
<p class="tagline">A living archive of Yoruba proverbs (òwe).</p>

{% set featured = owe | selectattr("featured") %}
{% if featured | length %}
  <h2>Starter set</h2>
  {% for entry in featured %}
    <article class="owe-card">
      <p class="owe-yoruba">{{ entry.text_yoruba }}</p>
      <p class="owe-meaning">{{ entry.figurative_meaning }}</p>
      <p class="tag-list">
        {% for t in entry.themes %}{{ t }}{% if not loop.last %}, {% endif %}{% endfor %}
        ·
        {% for s in entry.situations %}{{ s }}{% if not loop.last %}, {% endif %}{% endfor %}
      </p>
      <a href="/owe/{{ entry.slug }}/">Read more</a>
    </article>
  {% endfor %}
{% else %}
  <p>No entries published yet. Seed compilation is underway.</p>
{% endif %}
